data.title: Ysgol John Bright YJB
data.meta_description: Ysgol John Bright is a secondary school on Maesdu Road, Llandudno. It serves the state secondary education sector in the Llandudno area and has around 1200 pupils. The school was recently rebuilt and opened in September 2004.
